# Utility mods for Fabric 1.20.1

These are mods that are essential for creating, removing, and editing aspects of the game to create custom content and unique experiences for a modpack.


| Name | Links | Description | Alternatives |
|------|-------|-------------| --------------|
| Biome Replacer | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/biome-replacer) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/biome-replacer) | A quick way to get rid of a biome | - |
| CraftTweaker | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/crafttweaker) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/crafttweaker) | Change recipes, script events, add new commands, and change item properties with ZenScript | - |
| KubeJS | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/kubejs) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs) | Edit recipes, add new custom items, script world events through JavaScript | - |
| Lithostitched | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lithostitched) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/lithostitched) | Library mod with new configurability and compatibility enhancements for worldgen | - |
| Mob Control | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ohaydens-mob-control) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/mob-control) | Rule-based mob spawning and AI configuration. Closed Source. | - |
| Open Loader | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/open-loader) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/open-loader) | Allows data packs and resource packs to be applied globally across all save files in a game instance. | [Paxi](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/paxi) |
| Reliable Recipes | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/reliable-recipes) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/reliable-recipes) | Dynamic recipe and tag manipulation via simple JSON configuration | - |
| Reliable Remover | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/reliable-remover) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/reliable-remover) | Allows for completely removing items via simple JSON configuration. | [Item Obliterator](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/item-obliterator), though this mod was made to address critical issues of it. |
| Reliable Replacer | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/reliable-replacer) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/reliable-replacer) | Allows for replacing one block with another, both during worldgen and afterward. | [Block Swap](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/block-swap), though this mod was made to address critical issues of it. |
| Structurify | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/structurify) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/structurify) | GUI-based structure configuration | - |

\* - A must-have mod for nearly any modpack. Only in very rare circumstances should you not use this mod or an equivalent.

** - Prone to issues or conflicts with other mods